plot: Cher is the rich girl in town and she even lives in a castle with armored knight statues outside the front door! And the parties she throws are legendary.

Allison may only be 15 years old, but she already considers herself to be a jet-setter. She's the daughter of an affluent attorney who works with stars like Jermaine Dupri, TI, and Ludacris so she's used to hob-knobbing with celebrities and traveling all over the world.—Anonymous
